    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="row img-box-text">
                    <div class="col-md-12 header-1">
                        <h3 class="f-s-30">
                            Recruitment and Talent Management Solutions
                        </h3>
                        <span class="devider-center"></span>
                        <p class="f-s-18">
                            MVP Talent Market is an affiliate of MVP Recruitment, LLC and MVP Talent Optimization. 
                            These companies work in harmony to provide a full range of 
                            recruitment and talent management solutions. 
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="recruitment-logo-section">
                        <div class="recruitment-logo-section-main">
                            <div class="recruitment-logo-section-box">
                                <div class="img-area">
                                    <img src="~/New_Content/images/11.png" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-area">
                                    <h3>
                                        MVP Recruitment, LLC
                                    </h3>
                                    <p>
                                        Executive search firm for the healthcare industry. Assisting organizations with recruitment for critical and confidential needs for key management and leadership opportunities.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="recruitment-logo-section-box">
                                <div class="img-area">
                                    <img src="~/New_Content/images/12.png" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-area">
                                    <h3>
                                        MVP Talent Optimization
                                    </h3>
                                    <p>
                                        A consulting firm that assists organizations in identifying and building a talent strategy that aligns with their business goals. By utilizing HR analytics and behavioral data, we help organizations identify the internal drives and work preferences of their team members to ensure the right people are in the right position to achieve shared success.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-main">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="row img-box-text">
                    <div class="col-md-12 header-1">
                        <h3>
                            Inspired by MVP’s and The Greatness of Team Work.
                        </h3>
                        <span class="devider-center"></span>
                        <p class="f-s-18 text-center">
                            Co-Founders Jared Jackson and Gary Laakso have been teammates and best friends since 8th grade. Now, with over 30+ years of combined recruitment experience, they are seeking to impact the way organizations hire and inspire their workforce. As sports fans, we appreciate when teams come together to achieve their goals and believe so much can be learned by blending concepts used in professional sports into how companies view and build teams. We also draw inspiration from companies and business leaders who believe their people are the key to success. Please join us in our mission to help everyone
                            <ht class="">
                                Win At Work!
                            </ht>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                     
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
